Dialogue: 1,0:00:23.01,0:00:24.12,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,阿爾托你等等
Dialogue: 1,0:00:29.31,0:00:31.97,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,所以我不能讓你過去
Dialogue: 1,0:00:39.11,0:00:40.88,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,你就陪我一會吧
Dialogue: 1,0:00:42.63,0:00:43.97,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,真難纏
Dialogue: 1,0:00:49.46,0:00:50.53,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,薇爾梅小姐
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.90,0:01:18.30,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,厲害 厲害啊
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.78,0:01:22.48,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,這就是我的研究成果
Dialogue: 1,0:03:07.09,0:03:08.18,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,薇爾梅小姐？
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.69,0:03:11.29,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,這是 什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.30,0:03:15.19,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.35,0:03:17.61,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,奧布希蒂安老師 這究竟
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.55,0:03:22.98,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,哦 來得好
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.35,0:03:27.02,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,老 老師？
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.78,0:03:30.17,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,來 你們也來欣賞欣賞
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.09,0:03:33.42,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,如何 是不是很棒
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.85,0:03:35.76,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,看啊
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.32,0:03:46.80,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,堂堂惡魔竟向我下跪了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.30,0:03:52.28,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.25,0:03:54.61,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.92,0:03:56.90,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,怎麼
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.20,0:03:58.68,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,還沒明白嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:03:59.33,0:04:02.43,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,還以為你是個聰明的學生
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.08,0:04:04.59,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,可費勁了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.94,0:04:07.30,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,首先將瘋魔化魔術給固定好
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.63,0:04:10.34,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,然後把它凝縮成液體
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.51,0:04:11.77,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,費了我好大一番功夫
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.05,0:04:14.93,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,算是我特製的吧
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.53,0:04:20.27,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,再把它注射入體內 使得惡魔之力暴發失控
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.72,0:04:23.36,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,哪怕是「真」的 也成了這樣
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.23,0:04:28.13,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,要找用來實驗的小白鼠也很辛苦啊
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.44,0:04:30.86,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,竟然耗費了5個人
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.45,0:04:34.62,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,不過他們做得很棒
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.90,0:04:39.25,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,感謝他們 我的實驗大獲成功
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.77,0:04:44.18,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,您究竟在說點什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.17,0:04:48.93,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,還不懂嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.42,0:04:57.21,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,這一切都是我做的
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.77,0:05:00.05,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,阿爾托·戈爾德菲爾德同學
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.72,0:05:03.57,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,一 切？
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.35,0:05:09.13,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,沒錯 一切
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.66,0:05:18.62,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,這可是史上最大的災厄
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.62,0:05:21.38,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,豈有不利用的道理
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.77,0:05:43.86,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,原來
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.05,0:05:46.90,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,你也有情緒如此激動的一面
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.10,0:05:48.53,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,但你放心
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.73,0:05:50.25,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,我來給你展示
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.61,0:05:53.03,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,如何多加善用她吧
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.64,0:06:09.30,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,薇爾梅小姐
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.47,0:06:12.18,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.74,0:06:36.65,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,阿爾托…
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.72,0:06:41.75,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.82,0:06:45.29,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,彷彿整個人被困在水中
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.84,0:06:49.71,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,這裡又黑 又冷
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.58,0:06:51.87,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,空無一物
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.93,0:06:57.86,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,明明是我所期盼的
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.30,0:07:30.12,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,啊 對啊
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.28,0:07:40.47,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.38,0:07:44.38,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.40,0:07:52.40,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.62,0:08:20.84,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,變得越來越不祥了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.98,0:08:22.74,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,太荒謬了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.36,0:08:37.80,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,不可以的
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.48,0:08:45.90,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,薇爾梅小姐
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.04,0:08:49.08,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,…爾托
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.59,0:09:02.60,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,阿爾托…
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.26,0:09:06.35,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.92,0:09:10.50,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.26,0:09:12.46,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,回過神
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.52,0:09:15.89,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,身體已經做出行動了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.70,0:09:19.11,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.70,0:09:22.66,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,我可是
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.71,0:09:27.95,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,薇爾梅小姐的主人啊
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.76,0:09:39.23,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,阿爾托 我 我…
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.38,0:09:44.73,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,沒事…的
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.77,0:09:49.39,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,我 就在這裡
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.12,0:09:54.10,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,沒事…的
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.83,0:10:04.53,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,阿爾托
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.55,0:10:11.18,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,不會吧 死了…
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.57,0:10:13.45,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.00,0:10:18.66,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,阿爾托
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.19,0:10:24.20,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,不會讓你死的
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.77,0:10:29.56,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,世間唯獨你 我一定
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.89,0:10:49.65,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,金色的魔力
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.00,0:11:12.09,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,什麼鬼
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.85,0:11:17.04,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,連生死都能操控嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.33,0:11:20.69,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,這就是「真」的嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.39,0:11:24.21,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,真 真 真
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.56,0:11:26.71,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,真 真
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.29,0:11:28.40,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.76,0:11:30.29,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,為什麼事情會變成這樣
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.64,0:11:32.85,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,可惡 可惡 可惡
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.25,0:11:35.13,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.88,0:11:37.17,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,那 那是什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.17,0:11:40.84,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,少逗我了 你們一個個都
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.84,0:11:42.80,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,一口一個「真」
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.29,0:12:05.57,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,別小看我
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.40,0:12:07.34,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,我也
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.66,0:12:09.53,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,早就下定決心了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:12.56,0:12:13.50,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,如何
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.82,0:12:17.17,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,這是我獨門製出的「混合惡魔」
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.35,0:12:20.43,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,把數百隻下級魔不斷餵給它後
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.43,0:12:21.84,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,得到的究極一隻
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.44,0:12:24.13,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,哪怕是瘋魔化的你
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.37,0:12:26.36,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,我都能輕鬆碾碎
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.36,0:12:28.84,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,這就是我的研究
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.42,0:12:31.22,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,看好了廢物們
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.45,0:12:33.52,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,這就是我的實力
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.53,0:12:37.64,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,本來還想著養你的
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.06,0:12:39.29,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,罷了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:41.37,0:12:43.58,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,剁了你 碾碎你
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.69,0:12:47.53,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,把你混合進我的身體裡
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.62,0:13:02.58,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,為 為什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.58,0:13:03.59,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,就 就一拳
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.88,0:13:12.47,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,靠
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.60,0:13:13.55,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,可惡可惡
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.74,0:13:15.56,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,可惡 可惡
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.54,0:13:19.81,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,可惡啊
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.58,0:13:22.98,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,往天上逃就行了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.69,0:13:40.37,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.56,0:13:43.42,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,饒我一命
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.28,0:14:26.70,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,我不會要你命的
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.60,0:14:30.51,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,畢竟是阿爾托拚死守下來的一條命
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.87,0:14:46.06,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,咦 我這是…
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.77,0:14:50.57,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,阿爾托
Dialogue: 1,0:14:50.57,0:14:51.61,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,莉莉婭
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.61,0:14:54.53,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,太好了 太好了
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.07,0:15:00.18,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,我 我還以為你 再也不會醒過來了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.18,0:15:02.29,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,…別哭了 莉莉婭
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.52,0:15:05.22,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,阿爾托
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.22,0:15:07.54,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,傷口已經癒合了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.32,0:15:16.47,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,薇爾梅小姐？
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.32,0:15:27.15,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,後會 有期
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.62,0:15:41.41,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,你在這裡啊
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.93,0:15:43.76,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,你的傷勢怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.35,0:15:47.61,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,嗯 就像沒受過傷一樣 我還挺驚訝的
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.89,0:15:49.53,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,醫生也嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.37,0:15:51.12,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.63,0:15:54.10,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.82,0:15:58.59,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,那個 薇爾梅小姐
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.94,0:16:00.20,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,我當時
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.20,0:16:01.15,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.10,0:16:05.29,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,被我貫穿了心臟
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.28,0:16:07.35,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,死過一次了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.61,0:16:08.69,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,那 那
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.90,0:16:10.99,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,是薇爾梅小姐把我治好的吧
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.29,0:16:17.29,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,不完全對
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.08,0:16:23.68,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,現在你胸膛裡的
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.47,0:16:27.63,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,那顆心臟 是我用魔力編織出來的
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.54,0:16:38.32,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.38,0:16:43.85,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,你為什麼要道歉呢
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.20,0:16:47.02,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,不論你用的什麼辦法 你都是救了我啊
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.54,0:16:50.48,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,我的死亡也完全不是你的錯
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.94,0:16:53.95,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,而且你看 我現在生龍活虎
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.95,0:16:54.53,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.52,0:16:59.44,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,雖然也沒錯 但不是你想的那樣
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.95,0:17:04.66,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,現在你身體裡的 是我的心臟
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.96,0:17:09.58,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,真真正正的 惡魔的心臟
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.09,0:17:14.65,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,也就是說如果我死了 你也會死
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.05,0:17:23.64,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,等 等等 這意思不會是
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.12,0:17:26.98,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,嗯 要是你死了
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.62,0:17:29.89,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,我也會死
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.14,0:17:33.77,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,你都做了什麼啊
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.99,0:17:36.61,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,你可是惡魔啊
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.75,0:17:40.09,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,你的壽命本應該有上百年 上千年
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.99,0:17:45.79,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,我的
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.86,0:17:48.67,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,人類的壽命太短暫了
Dialogue: 1,0:17:52.77,0:17:53.94,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.02,0:18:01.74,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,之後 薇爾梅小姐就一句話也沒說了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.19,0:18:08.61,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,學生會會長
Dialogue: 1,0:18:08.88,0:18:11.58,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,據說她當時正跟一個疑似共犯的人戰鬥
Dialogue: 1,0:18:12.11,0:18:13.46,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,但沒抓到對方的尾巴
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.57,0:18:18.22,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,奧布希蒂安老師則被奧爾提基亞市的警察帶走了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.22,0:18:21.36,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,然後 這次的事情
Dialogue: 1,0:18:21.79,0:18:23.63,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,雖留下了許多謎團
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.14,0:18:26.06,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,也算是告一段落了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.68,0:18:34.16,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,痛
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.03,0:18:37.57,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,靠 到底發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.45,0:18:52.06,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,昏睡過去的學生們
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.73,0:18:54.50,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,也清醒了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.31,0:19:02.31,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,阿爾托 時間到了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:03.51,0:19:05.14,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,已經這麼晚了啊
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.80,0:19:09.43,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,這次事情後
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.72,0:19:11.34,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,發生了一些變化
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.42,0:19:14.07,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,現在變成我的心臟
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.37,0:19:16.59,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,需要薇爾梅小姐的魔力了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.10,0:19:22.07,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,身體怎麼樣 有沒有哪裡不舒服
Dialogue: 1,0:19:22.85,0:19:24.58,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,嗯 沒問題
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.54,0:19:27.97,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,然後 薇爾梅小姐她
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.42,0:19:30.58,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,變得話少了許多
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.41,0:19:32.65,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,那個 薇爾梅小姐
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.16,0:19:35.10,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.40,0:19:37.06,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,還是有哪裡不舒服是吧
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.63,0:19:39.96,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,為什麼這麼冷淡
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.21,0:19:44.00,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,為什麼…你都知道了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.59,0:19:47.72,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,我真的就是災厄 是怪物
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.18,0:19:49.85,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,我是不應該與你
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.94,0:19:52.23,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,待在一起的
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.28,0:19:55.02,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,你不害怕我嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.17,0:19:58.96,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,不是看到過了嗎 我的真身
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.22,0:20:00.62,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,可怕 又醜陋
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.98,0:20:02.79,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,是個無藥可救的怪物
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.50,0:20:04.96,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,哪 哪有
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.79,0:20:09.39,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,當然 把你身體搞成這樣 我會負起責任
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.21,0:20:12.22,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,你給我的那些魔力
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.79,0:20:15.69,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,我會將其轉化為惡魔之力傳回你的心臟
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.48,0:20:18.68,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,等到你的心臟完全穩定
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.92,0:20:21.12,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,雖然不知道要花上多少年
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.75,0:20:23.90,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,但把我該做的做完了我就會離開
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.13,0:20:26.86,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,我說過吧
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.31,0:20:28.85,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,我不能待在你身邊
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.74,0:20:32.02,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,我再隨便找本書鑽進去吧
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.26,0:20:36.29,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,這樣肯定對你也好
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.48,0:20:37.46,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,薇爾梅小姐
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.40,0:20:40.44,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,我會生氣的
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.50,0:20:43.94,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,你這孩子怎麼就不懂
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.25,0:20:46.47,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,我們是沒辦法像正常人那樣
Dialogue: 1,0:21:00.11,0:21:02.23,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,你 你突然做什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.10,0:21:07.81,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,魔力 沒有被吸走
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.14,0:21:13.08,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,我又怎麼…
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.21,0:21:17.15,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,怎麼會害怕你呢
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.14,0:21:20.00,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,但是我
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.45,0:21:26.25,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,沒有什麼但不但是
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.83,0:21:29.22,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,薇爾梅小姐是我的使魔
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.18,0:21:33.68,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,你要是不一直留在我身邊我會很頭痛的
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.36,0:21:37.08,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,好 好的
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.27,0:21:47.18,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,我要說的就這些
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.82,0:21:54.49,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,說說說到底
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.57,0:21:56.16,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,接吻這事情本來
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.16,0:21:59.79,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,就就只能是跟喜歡的人做的
